4pt"> the motorised vehicle driver is</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt"> held to be responsible</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt"> for a collision</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt"> unless they can prove otherwise.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">Adopting this measure here would make far more motorists pay due care and attention.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt; font-style:italic">November 2013</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p></div></body></html>